org.cloudgraph.hbase.graph

Class LocalEdgeRecognizerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.graph.LocalEdgeRecognizerContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluationContext

    public class LocalEdgeRecognizerContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements EvaluationContext
    Context which supports the evaluation and "recognition" of a given data graph entity sequence value by a binary expression tree, within the context of the expression syntax and a given HBase KeyValue map.

    A sequence uniquely identifies an data graph entity within a local data graph and is used to construct qualifier filters to return specific sequence-based column qualifiers and associated column values.

    Since:
    0.5.2
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    HBaseGraphAssembler, GraphSliceSupport
